USABILITY TEST PLAN

Project: MovieGo Mobile App

Objective:
Evaluate the usability of the MovieGo movie ticket booking application.

Participants:
5 users

Test Environment:
Mobile prototype developed in Figma

Metrics:

* Task completion rate
* Time taken per task
* Number of user errors
* User satisfaction score

Tasks:

1. Login/Register
2. Search for a movie
3. Select theatre
4. Choose seats
5. Make payment
6. View booking confirmation

Expected Outcome:
Identify usability issues and opportunities for design improvement.
